- `/app/src/index.css` - Foundation for the entire design system; all CSS custom variables, utility classes, and base resets must be defined here
- `/app/src/stores/useTryOnStore.ts` - Central Zustand store that drives the entire application flow (upload, processing, result states and all image data)
- `/app/src/components/upload/ImageDropZone.tsx` - Core reusable upload component with drag-and-drop, validation, and preview; both person and clothing uploads depend on it
- `/app/src/hooks/useTryOnGeneration.ts` - React Query hooks that bridge frontend state to the AI backend; handles mutation for starting generation and polling for results
- `/app/supabase/functions/virtual-try-on/index.ts` - The Supabase Edge Function that proxies requests to the Replicate API; the only server-side code in the entire application
